# Environment

## Client (Vite)
- `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`, `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` — safe for browser bundling.

## Server only
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`, `GEMINI_API_KEY`, and any future signing secrets — **never** prefixed with `VITE_`.

## Hygiene
- Update `.env.example` when adding variables. Never commit real `.env` files.
